flowchart TD
    attacker["Attacker"]
    app["Application Security<br/>Input validation, secure coding, auth"]
    os["OS Hardening<br/>SELinux/AppArmor, minimal services, sysctl"]
    kernel["Kernel Hardening<br/>KASLR, stack protector, seccomp"]
    boot["Secure Boot<br/>Signed bootloader, verified kernel, dm-verity"]
    hw["Hardware Security<br/>TrustZone, secure boot ROM, HW RNG"]
    first["First line of defense<br/>Most exposed to attacks<br/>Must validate all input"]
    trust["Trust anchor<br/>Hardest to compromise<br/>Hardware-based root of trust"]
    attacker -->|Attack entry| app
    app -->|If breached| os
    os -->|If breached| kernel
    kernel -->|If breached| boot
    boot -->|Final defense| hw
    app -.-> first
    hw -.-> trust
